---
import "../../../styles/home/home.css";
---

<div class="service-row section">
  <div class="service-text">
    <span class="service-tag">For Visual Control</span>
    <h3>WordPress Page Builders (Elementor)</h3>
    <p>
      Need to change colors, fonts, and layouts yourself? I set up a
      professional foundation using Elementor. I build the structure, and you
      get the keys to drag-and-drop changes whenever you want.
    </p>
    <div class="best-for-box">
      <strong>Best for:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Small Business Owners (DIY)</li>
        <li>Marketing Teams</li>
        <li>Startups needing quick launch</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="service-image">
    <img
      src="/assets/Icons/e-commerce-store-wordpress-website-create.png"
      alt="Elementor"
    />
  </div>
</div>
